title: Key Republican wants Ga. as early primary state — in 2028
description: Georgia Secretary of State Brad Raffensperger wants his state to become an early presidential primary host — just not in 2024, as President Joe Biden and the Democratic Party are pushing
author: BILL BARROW Associated Press

title: Lt. governor blasts media coverage of Georgia's election law after poll says 99% midterm voters had no issues
description: In an interview with Fox News Digital, Burt Jones slammed the media's coverage of Georgia's election law after a new poll showed 99% of Peach State voters had no issues in the midterms.
author: Joseph Wulfsohn

title: Ruben Gallego Looks to Maintain Early Momentum to Defeat Kyrsten Sinema
description: "The way Gallego holds the momentum so he stands a chance," a Democratic campaign strategist said. "It really is about all the allies across the state."
author: Adrian Carrasquillo
